cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image representation and retrieval, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) also suggests a possible connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Finally, the proposed extension to the encoding method involves a novel saliency measure, which could be related to neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
